s, et a été enterré à Ashbourne, Derbyshire, Angleterre."},"de":{"1184–1270":"1184–1270","1188–1298":"1188–1298","1215–1305":"1215–1305","1220–1300":"1220–1300","1153–1242":"1153–1242","1157–1188":"1157–1188","February 1220":"Februar 1220","1242":"1242","1220":"1220","1153":"1153","1184":"1184","1270":"1270","1305":"1305","1259":"1259","1215":"1215","1224":"1224","1157":"1157","1300":"1300","about 1215":"um 1215","1298":"1298","1188":"1188","about 1214":"um 1214","about 1188":"um 1188","Ashbourne, Derbyshire, England":"Ashbourne, Derbyshire, England","Ashbourne,Derbyshire,England":"Ashbourne, Derbyshire, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Als William de Cokayne 1184 in Ashbourne, Derbyshire, England geboren wurde, war sein Vater William de Cokayne 32 und seine Mutter Sarah Fitzaldecinder 28. Er hat um 1214 in Ashbourne, Derbyshire, England Alice d'Aubigny geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 2 Söhne. Er starb 1270 im Alter von 86 Jahren in seinem Geburtsort und wurde in Ashbourne, Derbyshire, England begraben."},"ht":{"1184–1270":"1184–1270","1188–1298":"1188–1298","1215–1305":"1215–1305","1220–1300":"1220–1300","1153–1242":"1153–1242","1157–1188":"1157–1188","February 1220":"February 1220","1242":"1242","1220":"1220","1153":"1153","1184":"1184","1270":"1270","1305":"1305","1259":"1259","1215":"1215","1224":"1224","1157":"1157","1300":"1300","about 1215":"about 1215","1298":"1298","1188":"1188","about 1214":"about 1214","about 1188":"about 1188","Ashbourne, Derbyshire, England":"Ashbourne, Derbyshire, England","Ashbourne,Derbyshire,England":"Ashbourne, Derbyshire, Angletè, United Kingdom"},"hu":{"1184–1270":"1184–1270","1188–1298":"1188–1298","1215–1305":"1215–1305","1220–1300":"1220–1300","1153–1242":"1153–1242","1157–1188":"1157–1188","February 1220":"1220. február","1242":"1242","1220":"1220","1153":"1153","1184":"1184","1270":"1270","1305":"1305","1259":"1259","1215":"1215","1224":"1224","1157":"1157","1300":"1300","about 1215":"1215 körül","1298":"1298","1188